  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below required thresholds, the assurance level is declared High and the decision is recorded as Accepted — constituting an overstatement of assurance inconsistent with the structural evidence (COMPOUND-03).",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-absolute-threshold",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-centrifugal-pump-hemolysis",
