      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for Class III VAD hemolysis prediction at MRL 5 must satisfy level 4 SQA including full version control, regression testing, and documented release procedures.",
      "rationale": "Version control is present but regression test suite covers only 40% of solver modules; release documentation is incomplete. Achieved level 2 falls two gradations below the required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
