      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be performed on the same device geometry and operating regime as the COU at level 4.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA benchmark pump geometry, which shares topology with the COU device but differs in impeller diameter and blade count. Geometric similarity is partial; no sensitivity analysis was performed to bound the extrapolation error. Achieved level 2."
