      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The turbulence and hemolysis constitutive models must be justified for VAD flow regimes with supporting literature or sensitivity analysis at level 4.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model is used without justification for the transitional flow regime present in the impeller passage; hemolysis model constants were taken from literature for a different pump class without re-calibration. Achieved level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
