      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but input parameter distributions for blood viscosity and hemolysis model exponents were not formally characterized; uniform distributions with ad hoc bounds were used. Factor not fully assessed; achieved level 1 assigned as epistemic gap."
