    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and the breadth of factors assessed collectively demonstrate sufficient confidence in the hemolysis predictions for regulatory submission. Assurance level is declared High based on the team's engineering judgment that the identified gaps are conservative. This rationale does not address the multiple factors achieving levels two or more gradations below required levels, nor the three unassessed factors at MRL 5.",
